  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in the role of a guardian of wildlife! In this captivating 3D toon-styled simulation game, you'll shape lush environments and carefully manage diverse species of animals to maintain harmony. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2967210/extras/2244073f887cd25c173cffeedb76d3dc.poster.avif?t=1730211585\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2967210/extras/2244073f887cd25c173cffeedb76d3dc.webm?t=1730211585\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2967210/extras/2244073f887cd25c173cffeedb76d3dc.mp4?t=1730211585\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Balance is key as you strategically place different creatures within the ecosystem, ensuring populations thrive without upsetting the delicate equilibrium. But beware, challenges arise as you navigate the intricate web of nature's cycles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock upgrades to bolster your animal's resilience against threats, from starvation to natural predators. As you progress, witness your creations flourish as you upgrade animals' ability to have more babies, search for food more effectively, and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2967210/extras/19c87618ebf5e547098d6856f148879c.poster.avif?t=1730211585\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2967210/extras/19c87618ebf5e547098d6856f148879c.webm?t=1730211585\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2967210/extras/19c87618ebf5e547098d6856f148879c.mp4?t=1730211585\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to embark on a journey of conservation and discovery? Play Wild Harmony now and experience the joy of nurturing nature in this delightful casual strategy simulation!\"</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in the role of a guardian of wildlife! In this captivating 3D toon-styled simulation game, you'll shape lush environments and carefully manage diverse species of animals to maintain harmony. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2967210/extras/2244073f887cd25c173cffeedb76d3dc.poster.avif?t=1730211585\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2967210/extras/2244073f887cd25c173cffeedb76d3dc.webm?t=1730211585\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2967210/extras/2244073f887cd25c173cffeedb76d3dc.mp4?t=1730211585\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Balance is key as you strategically place different creatures within the ecosystem, ensuring populations thrive without upsetting the delicate equilibrium. But beware, challenges arise as you navigate the intricate web of nature's cycles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock upgrades to bolster your animal's resilience against threats, from starvation to natural predators. As you progress, witness your creations flourish as you upgrade animals' ability to have more babies, search for food more effectively, and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2967210/extras/19c87618ebf5e547098d6856f148879c.poster.avif?t=1730211585\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2967210/extras/19c87618ebf5e547098d6856f148879c.webm?t=1730211585\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2967210/extras/19c87618ebf5e547098d6856f148879c.mp4?t=1730211585\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to embark on a journey of conservation and discovery? Play Wild Harmony now and experience the joy of nurturing nature in this delightful casual strategy simulation!\"</p>",
